name: Root.1
description: This is the first drop of the earth and body series, this series explores an original form and its final forms through mutation and manipulation, each root has 8 collectible metamorphs. Root.1 is an anthropoid grounded to her mother planet who morphs into 8 new forms, intertwined with her surrounding she is the embodiment of earths elements and the personification of nature. Grown from the soil beneath her feet she is root.1, a nymph. THIS IS BORN ON EARTH DAY.
